      "writtenOn": "2026-04-15T06:05:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The return check isn\u0027t required here as pldm_msgbuf accumulates errors on ctx and a failure in any operation (e.g. pldm_msgbuf_extract) poisons ctx-\u003eremaining to a negative sentinel, and then every subsequent operation returns early without touching its outputs. The final error is returned by pldm_msgbuf_complete_consumed(ctx), so no error is masked.",
